## Integration with Workflows

**Macro workflow alignment:**
- **Design**: Define tokens/contracts before UI/API work.
- **Build**: Use shared packages/tokens exclusively.
- **Verify**: Test visual regression and accessibility.

**Claudesy micro workflow:**
- **Context**: Check `packages/ui/tokens` and shared components.
- **Best Practice**: Validate against this rule.
- **Execution**: Only use approved stack and tokens.

**Genesis phases:**
- **Scaffold**: Define new tokens/components in shared packages.
- **Trinity Swarm**: Coordinate FE/BE/DevOps consistency.

