## Checklist for Tech Stack Work

**Frontend/UI:**
- [ ] Uses Tailwind utilities + design tokens (no hex).
- [ ] Components from `packages/ui` or new shared component proposed.
- [ ] Accessibility (ARIA, keyboard nav, contrast).
- [ ] Responsive (mobile-first).

**Backend/API:**
- [ ] Zod schema validation.
- [ ] Error responses standardized.
- [ ] OpenAPI docs updated.
- [ ] Rate limiting/auth enabled.

**Stack compliance:**
- [ ] Next.js/FastAPI/Prisma/Supabase/Tailwind only.
- [ ] pnpm/Turborepo workspace valid.
- [ ] Types align with `packages/types`.

---

## Refusal Triggers

Refuse proposals that:
- Use unapproved frameworks or versions.
- Hard-code colors/sizes instead of tokens.
- Duplicate shared component logic.
- Ignore accessibility or clinical readability.
